:name:
Haruspicy

:coretxt:
Mystical sight that some vampires posses.

:cost:
1 Instinct

:req:
Has seen someone die whom they didn't kill but were reason why they died.

:1:
Is able to see auras. 
This can be used to guess mood of people or get hints of some important event. Able to see those who walk in astral form

:2:
Ability to read someones mind or communicate. Can be resisted with \AbilityNameResist{}.

:3:
Ability to leave ones own body and travel in astral form. 

:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricMysticism
